<p>蓝牙</p>\n<p>谢谢推荐。</p>\n","last_modified":1645691183,"replies":19,"id":836153},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_large.png?m=1347578950","name":"icloud","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_normal.png?m=1347578950","title":"iCloud","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/icloud","topics":764,"footer":null,"header":"Store contacts, calendars, photos, music, books, apps and more in the cloud and access them on all your devices.","title_alternative":"iCloud","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_mini.png?m=1347578950","stars":159,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":430,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":483831,"username":"PrilgrimLi","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/PrilgrimLi","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f6/fe75/483831_mini.png?m=1611734761","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f6/fe75/483831_normal.png?m=1611734761","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f6/fe75/483831_large.png?m=1611734761","created":1586938204,"last_modified":1611734761},"last_reply_by":"juggtt213","last_touched":1645685177,"title":"iCloud，玄学般的产品","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/836111","created":1645672115,"deleted":0,"content":"- windows 11 里时刻显示正在上传 15 个文件，具体是啥也不知道。\r\n- 拷贝到 iCloud 网盘里的文件，立刻显示挂起，什么原因不知道。\r\n- mac 上传好的文件，iPad 上就是不更新，也不提供手动更新。\r\n- Pages 头一天晚上在 mac 上写好的文档，更新了，但是早晨在 iPad 上就是不更新新版本，删了个标点，立刻上传，然后把昨晚的内容覆盖了。\r\n\r\n\r\n丛稳定性来讲，iCloud 在苹果产品内部的互传都有抽风的时候。Apple One 拼车分的存储，真的不想浪费。\r\n\r\nGoogle Drive 都比 iCloud 在跨系统上稳定。Dropbox 大容量又太贵。国内网盘呢，呵呵。早前在百度网盘上传的文件说有敏感内容，就不能下载了。稍微个人一点的东西都不用百度盘了。88vip 里夸克送了 6t ，阿里领 4t ，移动联通也送云盘，但是真的不知道干啥。\r\n\r\n看来 Apple One 和 Google One 配合用是在所难免了。","content_rendered":"<ul>\n<li>windows 11 里时刻显示正在上传 15 个文件，具体是啥也不知道。</li>\n<li>拷贝到 iCloud 网盘里的文件，立刻显示挂起，什么原因不知道。</li>\n<li>mac 上传好的文件，iPad 上就是不更新，也不提供手动更新。</li>\n<li>Pages 头一天晚上在 mac 上写好的文档，更新了，但是早晨在 iPad 上就是不更新新版本，删了个标点，立刻上传，然后把昨晚的内容覆盖了。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>丛稳定性来讲，iCloud 在苹果产品内部的互传都有抽风的时候。Apple One 拼车分的存储，真的不想浪费。</p>\n<p>Google Drive 都比 iCloud 在跨系统上稳定。Dropbox 大容量又太贵。国内网盘呢，呵呵。早前在百度网盘上传的文件说有敏感内容，就不能下载了。稍微个人一点的东西都不用百度盘了。88vip 里夸克送了 6t ，阿里领 4t ，移动联通也送云盘，但是真的不知道干啥。</p>\n<p>看来 Apple One 和 Google One 配合用是在所难免了。</p>\n","last_modified":1645672115,"replies":19,"id":836111},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47527,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","stars":7712,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":524995,"username":"mky","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mky","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e379d168ae4f61e084f83ad6e0a1f654?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e379d168ae4f61e084f83ad6e0a1f654?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e379d168ae4f61e084f83ad6e0a1f654?s=73&d=retro","created":1608602706,"last_modified":1608602706},"last_reply_by":"EminemW","last_touched":1645684052,"title":"本 javer 最近接到组长给的人工智能的需求，倒腾了一番，也没啥思路，该怎么婉拒这个需求呢","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/836108","created":1645671740,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1645671740,"replies":19,"id":836108},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":181879,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answer